These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, hip-hop, ambient
1. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is between the fan of metal and the fan of r&b##2
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | ambient | r&b | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, lavender, green, grey
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Color   | lavender | light-blue | grey | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, monopoly, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing poker and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Game   | whist | poker | monopoly | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, ebony, emerald, green
