2. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes green is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Color   | ebony | turquise | green | emerald |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, siglo, dunhill, oliveros
1. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | oliveros | vegafina | dunhill | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
House: townhouse, tower, ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the tower house is on the far right##1
2. the tower house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
3. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| House   | ranch-style | townhouse | gothic-revival | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, march, september
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | september | may | march | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, eggplant, pumpkin, grapefruit
1. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| Food   | pumpkin | eggplant | grapefruit | garlic |

