.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
4. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Transport   | bike | taxi | airplane | van |

