.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
City: london, liverpool, hannover, new-york
1. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City   | new-york | london | hannover | liverpool |

