.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
City: nizza, venice, hamburg, boston
1. the person traveling to venice is the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| City   | hamburg | boston | venice | nizza |

