1. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival | victorian | futuristic |

 